    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is the ideal choice for a driver who values both performance and presentation. The exterior maintains a deep, glossy shine, showing only minor signs of road use like small stone chips on the leading edge. Inside, the interior is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the upholstery is well-preserved with only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster, and all electronic features\u2014from the infotainment to the climate control\u2014operate perfectly. Mechanically, this car has been fastidiously maintained with a complete service history. It recently received a fresh oil change and a new set of all-season tires, ensuring it is ready for the road immediately. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a solid, honest car that has been cared for with pride.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
